Package uk.ac.manchester.cs.mekon.owl.build

Provides an OWL-sanctioning-based section-builder plugin for MEKON models (see uk.ac.manchester.cs.mekon.owl for general description).

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    OBConfigVocab
    Vocabulary used in the OBSectionBuilder-definition section of the MEKON configuration file.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    OBAnnotationInclusion
    Represents a specification of a set of annotations to be copied from any relevant OWL entities to the corresponding frames-based entities that have been generated.
    OBAnnotations
    Responsible for copying annotations from OWL entities to the relevant generated frames-based entities.
    OBConceptAttributes
    Represents a set of attributes that will determine the details of the entities generated in the Frames Model (FM) for a particular OWL class.
    OBConceptGroup
    Represents a set of OWL classes to be included in the model building process.
    OBConceptHiding
    Specifies, for a particular section of concept-hierarchy, the set of concepts within that section for which the generated frames will be defined as "hidden".
    OBConcepts
    Represents the set of OWL classes that will be used in generating frames in the Frames Model (FM).
    OBEntities<E extends org.semanticweb.owlapi.model.OWLEntity,G extends OBEntityGroup,A extends uk.ac.manchester.cs.mekon.owl.build.OBAttributes<A>>
    Represents a set of OWL entities that will be used in generating entities in the Frames Model (FM).
    OBEntityGroup
    Represents a set of OWL entities defined via a single root-entity.
    OBEntityLabels
    Responsible for providing the labels for the frames-based entities that will be generated from named OWL entities.
    OBOptimisingSectionBuilder
    Specialisation of OBSectionBuilder that builds the OWL-derived section of the frames-based model in a manner that optimises both the initial classification and all subsequent reasoning.
    OBProperties
    Represents the set of OWL properties that will be used in generating slots in the Frames Model (FM).
    OBPropertyAttributes
    Represents a set of attributes that will determine the details of the entities generated in the Frames Model (FM) for a particular OWL property.
    OBPropertyGroup
    Represents a set of OWL properties to be included in the model building process.
    OBSectionBuilder
    Responsible for building a section of the Frames Model (FM) derived from a set of OWL ontologies via a standard "sanctioning" mechanism.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    OBAxiomPurgePolicy
    Specifies the policy that determines which axioms, if any, will be removed from the OWL model after the OWL-based model section has been built and the reasoner loaded.
    OBConceptHidingFilter
    Represents a filter that will be applied to the concepts specified by the scope of a concept-hiding specification.
    OBEntitySelection
    Specifies which concepts or properties are to be selected from of within a particular section of hierarchy.
    OBFrameSlotsPolicy
    Specifies the policy for frame-valued slot creation.
    OBSlotSources
    Specifies the types of constructs from which slots are to be derived.

Package uk.ac.manchester.cs.mekon.owl.build Description

Provides an OWL-sanctioning-based section-builder plugin for MEKON models (see uk.ac.manchester.cs.mekon.owl for general description).
